B? Should you pick C?

00:14:52.320 --> 00:14:56.640
Well, you obviously want to make the most
money. That's what you guys all want to do;

00:14:56.640 --> 00:15:02.240
right? We want you guys to make the most money.
So to accomplish that, you would want to be

00:15:02.240 --> 00:15:09.751
on the top of all these charts. So you want
to pick the highest or optimal eCPM at any

00:15:09.751 --> 00:15:14.640
given time, no matter what network. You want
to serve that ad network's ad at any given

00:15:14.640 --> 00:15:22.000
time. So what you want to do is called mediate.
